{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bd33dab13d","title":"给黄炎培的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d6b44e0a66","index":0,"year":1953,"month":5,"day":17,"articleId":"bd33dab13d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"533bf623d0","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"bd33dab13d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中国民主建国会召开的地方工商情况汇报会根据各地材料汇集的《资料简报》和《资料提要》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4d7809d813","type":"title","text":"给黄炎培的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"bd33dab13d"},{"id":"533bf623d0","type":"paragraph","text":"任之先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"bd33dab13d"},{"id":"0374a96417","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十六日惠书及附件收收到，甚谢。解决问题，应当由各有关方面先行协商，然后由政府加以择决；并且希望在不久时间内，对工商界未解问题作成一个草案，此事大概是可能的。此复","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"bd33dab13d"},{"id":"d86d8905f7","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"bd33dab13d"},{"id":"b9655b3214","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"bd33dab13d"},{"id":"cbe800fe77","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五三年五月十七日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"bd33dab13d"},{"id":"6acdcb184a","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]指黄炎培1953年5月16日给毛泽东的信。信中说，中国民主建国会于4月13日至30日召开了12个地方组织的工商情况汇报会，从汇报中看出各地工商业情况已有显著的好转，但好转的情况不平衡，还存在着不少问题。建议注意两点：一、必须有组织有领导地帮助各地工商业解决一切问题，这里所谓有组织、有领导，就是包括党委、政府、工会、税务、银行、工商联、民主团体等，把这些单位集合在一处，在党政根据总的方针指导下，任何问题都不难解决。二、处理任何问题，只有环绕着一个中心——搞好生产来活动，才是最有效的方法。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"bd33dab13d"}],"page":{"id":"6640500a67","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"bd33dab13d","start":169,"end":169}}}},"__N_SSG":true}